                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>1999-01-12</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>A fascinating story about the discovery of infrasonic communication between elephants, her experiences with elephants, and the implications of culling on these magnificient creatures. Payne maintains a foundation of integrity in her book which opens your heart to these beautiful animals. It is full of facts, anecdotes, stories and passion. I highly recommend buying this book as it is an incredible story and it is for the elephants!</span>
                  
              
